				<h2>BAYADA University for our home health care professionals</h2>
				<p>BAYADA believes in continuously improving our work through evaluation, education, and training. Through BAYADA University, our professionals can enhance their knowledge with free courses that supplement our one-on-one preceptor and <a href="bayada-way-mentoring.asp">mentoring programs</a>.</p>

				<p>In support of our company belief that our employees are our greatest asset, we also provide annual scholarships to be used toward continuing education through the <a href="bayada-way-presidential.asp">BAYADA Presidential Scholarship Program</a>. Additionally, our partnerships with several vendors and universities offer BAYADA employees exclusive educational and professional development opportunities, including tuition discounts.</p>

				<p>If you are a BAYADA home health care professional, please access our free online courses by clicking the appropriate link below.</p>

				<h3>Medcom Trainex, Inc.</h3>

				<p class="italics">Sample course topics: cardiac monitoring, infection control, pain management, pediatrics, wound care, and home health aide training</p>

				<p>Medcom is accredited as a provider of continuing nursing education by the American Nurses Credentialing Center Commission on Accreditation. Many of the courses offer contact hours for clinicians, and all home health aide courses equal one hour of in-service credit.</p>
				<p>If you do not have a BAYADA company email address, please <a href="medcom-login.asp">log in here &gt;&gt;</a></p>
				<p>If you have a BAYADA company email address, please <a href="https://portal.bayada.com/learnsharelinker.aspx">log in here &gt;&gt;</a></p>

				<h3>BAYADA University Learning Management System (LMS)</h3>

				<p class="italics">Sample course topics: OASIS competency, BAYADA Readmission Reduction Program, and Abbott Nutritionals partnership course</p>

				<p>BAYADA University LMS provides our Home Health (Medicare) field employees with access to various training topics.</p>

				<p>If you are a Home Health (Medicare) employee with a BAYADA company email address, please <a href="https://portal.bayada.com/learnsharelinker.aspx">log in here &gt;&gt;</a></p>
